sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: TC_019_1_CSMS: Retrieve all configuration keys
    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.7.1 - Core Profile - Configuration Happy Flow

    CS->>CP: 1. GetConfiguration.req (key = empty)
    Note right of CS: No specific keys requested → retrieve all

    CP-->>CS: 2. GetConfiguration.conf (configurationKey = [...all keys...])

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: Response must contain all required<br/>configuration keys from Core, Local Auth List Management,<br/>and Smart Charging profiles with correct accessibility (R/RW)
